description.narrative: C4D milestones achieved in 2020 mid-year: UNICEF has also supported the development of key strategic documents including the National Nutrition Communication Strategy, the Karamoja Communication Strategy; and the National Risk Communication and Social Mobilization Strategy for Covid-19. UNICEF has also supported the translation of the Key Family Care Practices counselling cards, fact sheets and flyer into 24 languages. Operationalization of the C4D Strategic shifts, specifically with regards to capacity strengthening of UNICEF internal capacity in C4D, strengthened capacity of key counterpart Ministry of Health through technical and operational support and through budget support to selected districts. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:30/06/2020
